nhc_headline: ...OCTAVE STILL HOLDING ON AS A TROPICAL STORM...
summary: ...OCTAVE STILL HOLDING ON AS A TROPICAL STORM... As of 2:00 AM MST Thu Oct 09 the center of Octave was located near 16.9, -111.7 with movement ENE at 18 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1004 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 40 mph.
